{"tid":2463432,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"玻璃保護貼係咪真係螢幕替死鬼？","createTime":"2021-03-26T16:34:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T18:16:02.000Z","uid":317288,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"71cce6726304a3d0d7d0c1d610a29045172a1f76","tid":2463432,"uid":317288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T16:34:08.000Z","msg":"次次換完過幾日啲邊位已經爆左<br />\n又時直頭都唔知幾時有撞到<br />\n換一次就三四十蚊 <br />\n隻隻牌子都吹到自己係9D12D高級鋼化玻璃<br />\n攞刀咭攞錘打都唔爆<br />\n但其實D邊位仲脆撚過支那人個心<br />\n今日換mon貼<br />\n啱啱部iphone喺手機架跌一跌落枱面<br />\n個mon貼又崩咗個邊<br />\n其實係咪應該用返舊式膠mon貼？"},{"pid":"22f691241ade97e6bb567e5734aabc67231f4c00","tid":2463432,"uid":317288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T16:42:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6e76decac1f1532af4de62a352eda7e72f4087a","tid":2463432,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T16:51:23.000Z","msg":"大牌子mon貼？"},{"pid":"9088287e7a387ffdb04f10120e2299236f2c17b9","tid":2463432,"uid":192732,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T16:56:55.000Z","msg":"咪玩啦，新手機個mon仲硬正過啲mon貼 <br />\n要mon 貼黎把撚"},{"pid":"a0bd88528b6cf486849bd2daec580b10713c1a61","tid":2463432,"uid":383914,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T17:00:01.000Z","msg":"試下用水凝貼膜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n似以前的膠mon貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔介意淘仔大把又平<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"863e5d67317b823c0078fcee5c77175df5f5e182","tid":2463432,"uid":343544,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T17:10:49.000Z","msg":"心理作用啫 買嚟得個睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmo